<title>USA: HCC Insurance sees Q4 EPS $0.30-shr or more.</title>
<headline>HCC Insurance sees Q4 EPS $0.30-shr or more.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1997-01-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>HCC Insurance Holdings Inc will report that it earned &quot;at least&quot; $0.30 per share in its fiscal fourth quarter, meeting analysts' estimates, the company's Chairman, Stephen Way, told Reuters.</p>
<p>Way would not provide a specific figure. He said the company would release the earnings next month.</p>
<p>The company is expected to earn $0.30 per share for the quarter based on the average estimate from analysts surveyed by First Call.</p>
<p>For the year, the estimate is $1.09 per share.</p>
